00:03:31,405 --> 00:03:32,760
KURŠĖNAI.

72
00:03:32,451 --> 00:03:34,098
in Kurshan, ye?

73
00:03:32,760 --> 00:03:34,723
in Kurshan.

74
00:03:36,332 --> 00:03:37,456
beyde.

75
00:03:39,943 --> 00:03:41,827
ven iz dos geven, gedenkt ir?

76
00:03:41,108 --> 00:03:43,869
gedenk ikh nit, di date gedenk ikh nit.

77
00:03:43,555 --> 00:03:46,732
un nokh dem vi ir zayt geven in Kuzh, in Kurshan

78
00:03:46,732 --> 00:03:50,535
zayt ir tsurikgekumen oykh in geto? tsu s'iz shoyn dos...

79
