80
00:03:51,179 --> 00:03:53,778
mit di meydl, mir UNK in Shavl

81
00:03:53,778 --> 00:03:54,247
⟨nit⟩ gekumen.

82
00:03:54,591 --> 00:03:58,486
ir gedenkt ven iz dos forgekumen, ven zayt ir aroys fun

83
00:03:58,486 --> 00:04:00,980
oyf di gantse tsayt fun Shavler geto?

84
00:04:01,442 --> 00:04:02,482
ikh gedenk nit.

85
00:04:03,062 --> 00:04:05,621
dos iz geven zumer, dos iz geven fri-?

86
00:04:04,294 --> 00:04:06,937
zumer, zumer iz dos geven, zumer.

87
00:04:07,517 --> 00:04:09,181
dos iz geven zumer, ye?

88
00:04:09,542 --> 00:04:12,033
un sh- dos iz shoyn geven nokh di kinder-aktsye?

89
00:04:11,652 --> 00:04:14,295
nokh di kinder-aktsye bin ikh glaykh UNK avek.

90
00:04:15,043 --> 00:04:16,775
ir geden-

91
00:04:15,077 --> 00:04:22,091
UNK me hot gezogt me vet nokh firn vayter un vayter, zog ikh: "ay, ikh vel aroysgeyn, prubirn dem mazl".

92
00:04:22,317 --> 00:04:26,648
ir gedenkt dem tog ven ir hot zikh bashlosn avekgeyn oyf di gantse tsayt fun geto?

93
00:04:26,704 --> 00:04:28,436
⟨nu⟩ ikh gedenk dos nit.

94
00:04:29,202 --> 00:04:32,419
ir hot gezogt ayere shkheynim mit velkhe...

95
00:04:31,362 --> 00:04:43,050
keyn eynem hob ikh nit gezogt. me hot mir gezukht in geto. afile UNK fun arbet fun aerodrom bin ikh antlofn dokh. oy, iz gekumen der BAULEITER un gezogt: "vu iz FRAU Shneyder?"

96
00:04:44,710 --> 00:04:48,079
zogn zey: "zi iz avek oyf der arbet un zi iz nit gekumen".

97
00:04:47,713 --> 00:04:50,255
vu hot er aykh gezukht? in in ge-?

98
00:04:49,165 --> 00:04:54,913
in geto, hobn zey gezogt, vayle aza hobn zey nit gehat fun froyen ver zol geyn oyf di dekher.

99
00:04:56,742 --> 00:04:59,683
az ir ir hot UNK gezogt az oyf di dekher

100
00:04:59,683 --> 00:05:02,186
hot ir gearbet tsuzamen mit an and-

101
00:05:01,146 --> 00:05:03,620
mit mit He- mit Hena.

102
00:05:03,643 --> 00:05:04,919
mit He-?

103
00:05:03,694 --> 00:05:05,747
Henke Fisher.

104
00:05:05,719 --> 00:05:08,010
un Hene Fisher iz

105
00:05:08,010 --> 00:05:09,189
farblibn?

106
00:05:09,195 --> 00:05:10,572
zi ⟨iz⟩ farblibn in geto.

107
00:05:10,545 --> 00:05:12,311
zi iz farblibn in geto?

108
00:05:12,402 --> 00:05:16,159
az ir zayt avek hot zi nokh in geto far-, iz zi farblibn in geto?

109
00:05:18,763 --> 00:05:22,756
zogt mir, ir zayt avek arbetn oyfn aerodrom ven ir zayt avek fun geto?

110
00:05:22,543 --> 00:05:25,659
ye, fun aerodrom bin avek shoyn aroysgelofn.

111
00:05:25,513 --> 00:05:28,156
vu zayt ir avek fun aerodrom?

112
00:05:27,977 --> 00:05:33,236
oto do in ŠIAU- do in Shavl hob ikh gehat a bakantn fun undzer shtetl.

113
00:05:34,879 --> 00:05:38,197
nu, zogt er, kum tsu geyn bay mir.

114
00:05:38,068 --> 00:05:39,665
dos iz geven a UNK?

115
00:05:38,878 --> 00:05:40,188
oykh a litviner.

116
00:05:40,380 --> 00:05:42,956
vi iz, zayn familye-nomen gedenkt ir oder a nomen?

117
00:05:43,080 --> 00:05:43,614
darf zayn...

118
00:05:44,430 --> 00:05:45,487
zayn nomen

119
00:05:45,544 --> 00:05:47,242
UNK zikh tsu, moment...

120
00:05:48,092 --> 00:05:49,402
UNK vi...

121
00:05:50,202 --> 00:05:51,360
PETROŠIUS!

122
00:05:51,467 --> 00:05:54,195
yo, PETROŠIUS JONAS.

123
00:05:51,501 --> 00:05:53,233
dos iz geven a familye-nomen?

124
00:05:55,163 --> 00:05:57,351
un JONAS iz geven zayn nomen?

125
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:57,958
ye.

126
00:06:00,208 --> 00:06:13,364
un mit di vayb bin ikh fun eyn shtetl geven. ye. zogt zi: "dervayl vestu zayn bay im un Jonas vet forn in vu mitn velosiped un vet krign far dir an ort", iz...

127
00:06:03,246 --> 00:06:04,674
fun Shvekshne?

128
00:06:13,607 --> 00:06:15,103
vi a dinst, nu.

129
00:06:16,628 --> 00:06:18,765
in dorf tsu arbetn.

130
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:24,249
un vu vi hot geheysn JONAS PETROŠIUSes froy?

131
00:06:24,525 --> 00:06:25,464
ONA.

132
00:06:25,555 --> 00:06:28,384
un ir hot ir gekent nokh fun di tsaytn fun Shvekshne?

133
00:06:27,681 --> 00:06:30,510
fun Shvekshne, mir hobn zikh gehodevet tsuzamen UNK

134
00:06:36,675 --> 00:06:41,073
un ir hot zikh az ir hot zikh gehodevet tsuzamen hot ir zikh gekhavert zikh, geshpilt tsuzamen?

135
00:06:40,573 --> 00:06:43,419
ye, ⟨me hot⟩ geshpilt, UNK geven a shtub lebn a shtub.

136
00:06:43,527 --> 00:06:46,265
a sakh yidn hobn gehat azelkhene

137
00:06:46,265 --> 00:06:49,595
batsiungen mit litviner az UNK zey hobn zikh geshpilt tsuzamen?

138
00:06:49,821 --> 00:06:55,502
nu dos iz... UNK geven UNK ikh veys nit, a kleyne shtetele, vos vu vos me shpilt zikh ale tsuzamen, kinder.

139
00:06:56,723 --> 00:07:00,261
un vi iz ONA gekumen in Shavl, zi hot khasene gehat?

140
00:06:59,946 --> 00:07:02,842
zi hot khasene gehat mit ir man, mit JONASn...

141
00:07:03,642 --> 00:07:06,471
az ir flegt fun tsayt tsu tsayt antloyfn

142
00:07:06,527 --> 00:07:09,409
fun di arbets-brigades flegt ir bazukhn

143
00:07:09,409 --> 00:07:11,415
di familye PETROŠIUS?

144
00:07:11,050 --> 00:07:12,022
ye.

145
00:07:12,535 --> 00:07:18,401
lebn ban oto do hobn zey gelebt in oyf a rog, fleg ikh ⟨op⟩tsyen tsu fus.

146
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:21,134
in vosere badingungen hobn zey gelebt?

147
00:07:21,613 --> 00:07:24,408
in vosere badingungen, zey hobn gehat a hoyz, a dire?

148
00:07:23,588 --> 00:07:25,812
zey hobn gehat, a shtibl hobn zey gehat.

149
00:07:25,812 --> 00:07:27,052
un er flegt ha-

150
00:07:27,052 --> 00:07:28,695
brukirn di gasn.

151
00:07:28,566 --> 00:07:29,690
in Shavl?

152
00:07:29,258 --> 00:07:30,163
ye.

153
00:07:31,047 --> 00:07:34,264
un zey flegn aykh oykh helfn mit shpayz?

154
00:07:33,662 --> 00:07:36,103
mit shpayz hobn zey mir nit gekent helfn.

155
00:07:36,312 --> 00:07:38,331
vayl zey zaynen geven oreme mentshn.

156
00:07:39,180 --> 00:07:42,701
nor az ikh fleg arayngeyn zey flegn haltn in esn flegn zey mir oykh gebn.

157
00:07:43,213 --> 00:07:45,772
aykh flegt oyskumen tsu shlofn bay zey oykh?

158
00:07:45,306 --> 00:07:46,346
yo.

159
00:07:46,285 --> 00:07:48,557
an- antloyfndik fun geto?

160
00:07:48,175 --> 00:07:51,358
ye. un antlofn fun geto bin ikh dortn geven.

161
00:07:51,195 --> 00:07:58,091
ober azoy, nisht nisht ni- nokh far dem, ven ir flegt nokh zayendik in geto aroysgeyn oyf a?..

162
00:07:57,304 --> 00:07:58,884
fleg ikh oykh avekgeyn.

163
00:07:58,418 --> 00:08:01,770
un es flegt pasirn az ir flegt shlofn bay PETROŠIUSn dan oykhet?

164
00:08:01,557 --> 00:08:02,546
ye.

165
00:08:02,417 --> 00:08:04,874
es flegt pasirn az ir flegt durkhlozn a nakht?..

166
00:08:03,261 --> 00:08:07,760
ye. ikh fleg aroys fun der geto mir zoln visn vu mir haltn oyf der velt.

167
00:08:07,851 --> 00:08:09,060
ir farshteyt?

168
00:08:09,100 --> 00:08:11,996
vos vos me vet nokh ton mit undz, veyst dokh?

169
00:08:12,542 --> 00:08:13,498
⟨veyst ir⟩ dokh.

170
00:08:13,504 --> 00:08:18,999
ir hot gezogt az ir ⟨es hot⟩ pasirt, es flegt pasirn az ir ir flegt nekhtikn bay LUNSKIENĖn?

171
00:08:19,056 --> 00:08:25,395
es flegt pasirn az ir flegt nekhtikn bay PETROŠIUSn... s'iz geven efsher andere litviner bay velkhn ir flegt nekhtikn?

172
00:08:21,503 --> 00:08:22,880
ye.

173
00:08:26,008 --> 00:08:29,073
aroysgeyendik fun geto, tsu nor bay di tsvey mishpokhes?

174
00:08:28,978 --> 00:08:33,683
ikh fleg nokh hobn nokh a a por UNK, nemen gedenk ikh nit, oykh in dorf.

175
00:08:33,683 --> 00:08:35,165
fleg ikh dortn shlofn.

176
00:08:34,952 --> 00:08:36,785
nisht vayt fun Shavl?

177
00:08:36,403 --> 00:08:40,514
yo, oykh oyf oyf aerodrom zayt, nokh eyne, GELEŽINIENĖ.

178
00:08:40,470 --> 00:08:41,932
GELEŽINIENĖ?

179
00:08:41,297 --> 00:08:42,455
ye.

180
00:08:42,124 --> 00:08:44,598
 zi flegt aykh oykhet nemen, ye?

181
00:08:44,368 --> 00:08:45,307
ye.

182
00:08:46,444 --> 00:08:50,589
un in vosere badingungen hot zi ge-, zi hot gehat kinder, a man, di GELEŽINIENĖ?

183
00:08:50,089 --> 00:08:51,773
zi hot nit gehat keynem nit.

184
00:08:51,773 --> 00:08:54,538
der man iz geshtorbn un keyn kinder hot zi nit gehat.

185
00:08:55,843 --> 00:08:58,891
un ir flegt bay ir nekhtikn oykh, ye?

186
00:08:58,257 --> 00:09:01,828
nekhtikn fleg ikh un nokh dem geyn oyf aerodrom.

187
00:09:02,188 --> 00:09:04,210
ay, oyf dem kumendikn tog?

188
00:09:04,210 --> 00:09:06,283
zikh tsu eynikn tsu di

189
00:09:06,306 --> 00:09:07,298
tsu di brig-...

190
00:09:06,492 --> 00:09:08,421
tsu der arbet fleg ikh kumen.

191
00:09:08,421 --> 00:09:10,707
un ikh hob gehat a oyfzeer,

192
00:09:10,707 --> 00:09:12,257
hot er geheysn,

193
00:09:13,849 --> 00:09:14,568
ay,

194
00:09:15,638 --> 00:09:16,611
a daytsh!

195
00:09:16,397 --> 00:09:17,656
a daytsh, ye?

196
00:09:17,848 --> 00:09:18,680
ye.

197
00:09:18,680 --> 00:09:20,778
iz es, er flegt mikh aroyslozn.

198
00:09:21,105 --> 00:09:25,773
ah, er flegt aykh a- a- aroyslozn geyn dortn in di, bay di litviner?

199
00:09:25,270 --> 00:09:28,620
ye, zogt er: "gey avek, Lina, gey avek un"

200
00:09:28,620 --> 00:09:31,072
"zay dortn, nokh dem vest kumen tsu der arbet".

201
00:09:31,483 --> 00:09:33,046
aha, er flegt aykh ge-

202
00:09:32,023 --> 00:09:36,371
Neymant, Neymant, itster hob ikh zikh dermont. der daytsh hot geheysn Neymant.

203
00:09:33,981 --> 00:09:35,510
der daytsh iz geven

204
00:09:36,445 --> 00:09:37,755
Neymant, ye?

205
00:09:37,305 --> 00:09:38,176
ye.

206
00:09:39,533 --> 00:09:40,910
un,

207
00:09:41,153 --> 00:09:45,956
un far vos far vos hot ir zikh ayngekoyft azelkhene gute simpatye bay dem daytshn?

208
00:09:44,967 --> 00:09:48,870
ikh veyst nit. er er hot zeyer... flegt mir esn gebn un altsding.

209
00:09:48,870 --> 00:09:50,397
un er flegt mir alts zogn:

210
00:09:50,397 --> 00:09:52,672
"hob geduld, ⟨UNK⟩vil zikh nit".

211
00:09:52,813 --> 00:09:55,473
zogt er: "di krig iz farshpilt".

