00:09:56,442 --> 00:09:59,645
er iz aleyn a daytsh geven. zogt er: "ot ikh bin a komunist"

213
00:09:59,645 --> 00:10:01,813
"hot men mir azoy getribn fun Daytshland",

214
00:10:01,813 --> 00:10:03,438
"gebrakht do in Lite".

215
00:10:03,883 --> 00:10:04,876
zogt er:

216
00:10:04,876 --> 00:10:06,412
"darf ikh aykh oyfpasn".

217
00:10:06,412 --> 00:10:07,775
ober er flegt

218
00:10:09,283 --> 00:10:10,593
keyn zakh nit zogn.

219
00:10:10,785 --> 00:10:12,787
un keyn shlekhts hot, flegt er key-?

220
00:10:10,836 --> 00:10:14,166
a guter mentsh biz gor.

221
00:10:14,166 --> 00:10:15,077
a gold

222
00:10:15,077 --> 00:10:16,095
iz er geven,

223
00:10:16,455 --> 00:10:20,229
der daytsh. un esn, me flegt brengen esn, flegt er

224
00:10:21,214 --> 00:10:23,351
zogn: "na, Lina, es op",

225
00:10:23,610 --> 00:10:24,484
ale mol.

226
00:10:24,370 --> 00:10:26,018
er fleg aykh rufn Lina?

227
00:10:25,433 --> 00:10:27,201
Lina flegt er mir rufn.

228
00:10:27,201 --> 00:10:28,008
Lina.

229
00:10:28,150 --> 00:10:29,477
Lina Shneyder.

230
00:10:29,803 --> 00:10:32,395
ah, vayl Leye iz im geven shver tsu zogn?

231
00:10:31,930 --> 00:10:33,105
ye, Lina.

232
00:10:33,145 --> 00:10:38,961
iz es er. un nokh dem iz nokh eyner geven ober ikh bin nit geven bay im. iz er hot geheysn Shults.

233
00:10:39,287 --> 00:10:40,411
ŠULCAS.

234
00:10:41,278 --> 00:10:43,010
flegt er hargenen

235
00:10:43,303 --> 00:10:44,950
az s'iz shreklekh geven.

236
00:10:45,700 --> 00:10:46,976
der Shults, ye?

237
00:10:47,067 --> 00:10:48,748
ober ir zayt bay im nisht geven?

238
00:10:48,484 --> 00:10:49,203
ikh bin nit

239
00:10:49,699 --> 00:10:50,250
UNK bay im.

240
00:10:49,952 --> 00:10:52,730
ir ir flegt ale mol arbetn bay Neymantn?

241
00:10:52,332 --> 00:10:55,886
ye, ikh bin... ale ale in der fri er flegt nemen fun aerodrom.

242
00:10:56,112 --> 00:10:58,029
flegt er glaykh tsu im nemen mir.

243
00:10:58,407 --> 00:11:00,611
bay im iz mir gut geven tsu arbetn.

244
00:11:00,482 --> 00:11:02,737
ir hot ge-, ir hot gekent daytsh dan?

245
00:11:02,592 --> 00:11:04,375
nu, a bisl hob ikh gekent.

246
00:11:05,173 --> 00:11:09,909
az ir fl- az ir hot gelebt in Meml, hobn di bafelkerung geredt merer daytsh tsu litvish?

247
00:11:09,308 --> 00:11:16,339
nu flegn redn UNK geven litviner, hobn geredt litvish un s'iz geven mit daytshn, flegn redn tsu daytshn, ober me hot gekent farshteyn...

248
00:11:17,138 --> 00:11:19,747
ir hot gekent f- farshteyn di daytshe UNK?

249
00:11:18,943 --> 00:11:19,983
yo.

250
00:11:20,580 --> 00:11:23,054
iz itster dertseylt mir, az ir zayt

251
00:11:23,820 --> 00:11:26,348
UNK geven geredt mit PETROŠIUSn?

252
00:11:26,348 --> 00:11:29,366
az ir geyt avek tsu zey az ir antloyft fun geto?

253
00:11:29,187 --> 00:11:30,278
⟨ye⟩

254
00:11:30,722 --> 00:11:32,285
azoy UNK s'iz geven

255
00:11:32,359 --> 00:11:34,752
a tog, zog ikh tsu ir,

256
00:11:34,752 --> 00:11:36,403
zog ikh: "ONA, AŠ ATEISIU".

257
00:11:36,325 --> 00:11:37,837
dos heyst, "ikh vel kumen".

258
00:11:37,438 --> 00:11:38,934
ye, "ikh vil kumen".

259
00:11:39,008 --> 00:11:40,386
zogt zi: "kum".

260
00:11:40,408 --> 00:11:42,427
zogt zi: "ober Jonas vet kumen".

261
00:11:42,602 --> 00:11:45,957
"ikh hob ", zog ikh, "ikh hob zikh tsuzamengepakt di zakhn"

262
00:11:45,957 --> 00:11:46,983
"a bisl".

263
00:11:47,040 --> 00:11:50,443
 zogt zi: "nu, ikh mit Jonas ⟨veln⟩ onkumen".

264
00:11:51,225 --> 00:11:54,065
es tsu durkhshtopn dem tshemodan.

265
00:11:53,925 --> 00:11:55,201
durkhn vos?

266
00:11:54,065 --> 00:11:56,991
durkhn shtekhl-drot.

267
00:11:55,815 --> 00:11:57,294
durkhn shtekhl-drot.

268
00:11:57,148 --> 00:11:57,904
nu,

269
00:11:57,904 --> 00:12:00,737
iz g⟨UNK⟩, hot men genumen shtupn,

270
00:12:01,030 --> 00:12:03,791
"HALT, HALT", hot genumen shrayen a daytsh.

271
00:12:04,101 --> 00:12:07,149
iz er mit ir zaynen arayn in vaser,

272
00:12:07,543 --> 00:12:09,877
in taykh, dortn iz glaykh der taykh

273
00:12:09,877 --> 00:12:10,662
geven.

274
00:12:10,662 --> 00:12:13,983
un ikh bin tsurik avek in geto mitn tshemodan in der nakht.

275
00:12:14,344 --> 00:12:15,992
nu un, ot azoy.

276
00:12:15,272 --> 00:12:19,012
un di zakh hot aykh gelungen sof-kol-sof aribergebn?

277
00:12:19,103 --> 00:12:19,974
neyn.

278
00:12:20,031 --> 00:12:21,763
vayle er hot genumen shrayen: "HALT".

279
00:12:22,022 --> 00:12:25,391
un ir zayt aroys un ayere zakhn zenen geblibn in geto?

280
00:12:25,482 --> 00:12:28,277
neyn, ikh bin nit aroys, ikh bin tsurik arayn in geto.

281
00:12:27,844 --> 00:12:30,369
yo, ober az ir zayt aroys dem... nokh a mol.

282
00:12:30,358 --> 00:12:32,664
nokh a mol UNK mir shoyn nit gekhapt.

283
00:12:32,687 --> 00:12:34,841
dem tsveytn mol hot men mir shoyn nit gekhapt.

284
00:12:34,476 --> 00:12:36,545
un ir hot durkhgegebn dem tshemodan?

285
00:12:35,877 --> 00:12:38,250
durkhgegebn Jonasn dem tshemodan.

286
00:12:38,037 --> 00:12:41,473
Aha, iz Jonas... iz ayere zakhn zaynen avek frier far aykh?

287
00:12:42,745 --> 00:12:46,451
ot ot, vos a far a zakhn hot ir...vos far a zakhn zaynen geven?..

288
00:12:45,428 --> 00:12:49,542
nu, di zelbike kleyder, shikh, vos far a zakh hob ikh gekent trogn...

289
00:12:49,542 --> 00:12:51,919
altsding hobn zey dokh tsugenumen fun undz do.

290
00:12:52,684 --> 00:12:55,980
di di mebl mit altsding hot men dokh undz tsugenumen.

291
00:12:55,980 --> 00:13:05,236
keyn zakh hot UNK dokh nit gelozn. vi mir shteyen, UNK ongeton un vayter dokh UNK. nu un vos mitgenumen, a deke mit a dos, vayter dokh keyn zakh nit gehat.

292
00:13:05,236 --> 00:13:07,477
ober di zelbike, a kleydl, a shukh...

293
00:13:07,939 --> 00:13:09,873
iz dos iz alts geven in tshemodan.

294
00:13:09,424 --> 00:13:10,464
ye.

295
00:13:10,369 --> 00:13:15,020
un az az iz zayt gevunen, gekumen tsu PETROŠIUSn iz der tshemodan shoyn geven bay zey?

296
00:13:14,385 --> 00:13:15,357
ye.

297
00:13:15,195 --> 00:13:20,943
un vi hobn zey aykh oyfgenumen, di PETROŠ-, PETROŠIUS az ir zayt gekumen oyf zey oyf shtendik?

298
00:13:20,460 --> 00:13:23,106
keyn zakh nit. oyf shtendik bin ikh nit gekumen.

299
00:13:23,106 --> 00:13:26,630
er hot gezogt: "ikh vel forn in dorf un ikh vel gefinen far dir alts eyns arbet".

300
00:13:26,704 --> 00:13:28,976
dos heyst, er hot aykh oyfgenumen tsaytvaylik?

301
00:13:28,442 --> 00:13:32,725
tsaytvaylik, nu UNK oyfn dorf hot er gekrign zumer keyn arbet?

302
00:13:32,725 --> 00:13:37,745
me zukht dokh mentshn me zol arbetn. un nokh dem hob ikh zikh ayngelebt mit mit eyne un bay...

303
00:13:37,745 --> 00:13:39,067
mit KAUŠIENĖ.

304
00:13:39,546 --> 00:13:41,601
un zi hot mir gehaltn di gantse tsayt.

305
00:13:41,520 --> 00:13:44,771
un v- vi hot ir zikh bakant mit di KAUŠIENĖn?

306
00:13:44,625 --> 00:13:47,313
nu er hot gezogt UNK, "ikh vel dir gebn", zogt zi.

307
00:13:47,313 --> 00:13:48,821
d-, a meydl.

308
00:13:49,063 --> 00:13:52,314
a nit keyn khasene gehate UNK veyst dokh,

309
00:13:52,540 --> 00:13:53,617
zogt zi.

310
00:13:53,617 --> 00:13:56,567
nu zi, zi vil nit geyn, zi vil nit forn in Daytshland.

311
00:13:56,775 --> 00:13:59,269
zogt zi: "beser geyn in dorf arbetn

312
00:13:59,269 --> 00:14:01,410
zi zol nit darfn forn in Daytshland".

313
00:14:01,973 --> 00:14:03,317
nor farn esn.

314
00:14:03,475 --> 00:14:06,523
nu ⟨iz⟩ zogt zi: "nu to zolstu zi brengen tsu firn".

315
00:14:06,597 --> 00:14:09,476
er hot genumen dem velotsiped un hot gebrakht mikh tsu firn.

316
00:14:08,976 --> 00:14:11,889
vos heyst, aykh oyfn ram avekgezetst?

317
00:14:11,980 --> 00:14:13,628
oyfn, oyfn ram.

318
00:14:13,617 --> 00:14:15,889
aha, er hot aleyn gefirt un ir hot gezesn...

319
00:14:14,747 --> 00:14:16,783
ye, er hot mikh avekgefirt.

320
00:14:16,384 --> 00:14:18,825
in vos, in vos far a dorf iz dos geven?

321
00:14:19,202 --> 00:14:21,491
KUŽIAI, SMILTINIŲ KAIMA.

322
00:14:23,792 --> 00:14:25,220
in KUŽIAI, ye?

323
00:14:24,636 --> 00:14:25,541
ye.

324
00:14:26,408 --> 00:14:28,275
SMILTINIŲ KAIMAS.

325
00:14:28,095 --> 00:14:29,337
tsu KAUŠIENĖn?

326
00:14:29,023 --> 00:14:30,395
ye, bay KAUŠIENĖn.

327
00:14:30,407 --> 00:14:32,479
zogt mir azoy, di KAUŠIENĖ

328
00:14:32,479 --> 00:14:34,485
hot gevust az ir zayt a yidishe?

329
00:14:34,035 --> 00:14:34,991
neyn.

330
00:14:34,980 --> 00:14:35,716
neyn...

331
00:14:35,773 --> 00:14:37,252
keyner hot nit gevust.

332
00:14:36,938 --> 00:14:39,463
vos far a nomen hot ir gehat bay KAUŠIENĖn?

333
00:14:39,334 --> 00:14:44,627
LEONGINA TEODORA ADOMAITYTĖ. ot hob do do d- dem dokument fun galekh.

334
00:14:44,802 --> 00:14:47,698
oh der galekh hot aykh

335
00:14:46,759 --> 00:14:48,958
der galekh hot nokh dem zikh dervust.

336
00:14:48,958 --> 00:14:55,882
az er hot zikh dervust, az zi hot gehat moyre. eyne hot gezogt: "az zi geyt nit in tifle, ver iz zi azoyne?"

337
00:14:57,525 --> 00:14:58,855
hot zi moyre gehat.

338
00:14:58,855 --> 00:15:00,843
me shist dokh op di gantse mishpokhe.

339
00:15:01,626 --> 00:15:02,852
zogt zi:

340
00:15:02,858 --> 00:15:11,205
"ikh hob moyre". "az du host moyre", zog ikh, "darf men nit, gey ikh tsurik in Shavl". in Shavl bin ikh avek baym galekh.

341
00:15:10,671 --> 00:15:12,015
bay velkhn galekh?

342
00:15:11,616 --> 00:15:13,264
bay KLEIBA.

343
00:15:13,810 --> 00:15:16,656
KLEIBA, ot iz dokh ongeshribn zayn nomen mit altsding.

344
00:15:16,982 --> 00:15:19,203
dertseyl ikh ir, er hot gevust

345
00:15:19,294 --> 00:15:20,486
az s'iz do,

346
00:15:20,644 --> 00:15:22,190
az ikh bin a yidishe.

347
00:15:21,775 --> 00:15:22,883
KLEIBA?

348
00:15:22,399 --> 00:15:23,231
ye.

349
00:15:23,091 --> 00:15:24,317
fun vanent?

350
00:15:24,176 --> 00:15:28,569
fun vanent er hot gevust... mistome hot ver gezogt vayl es dortn zaynen geven yidishe bay im.

351
00:15:28,778 --> 00:15:29,897
bay KLEIBAn?

352
00:15:29,689 --> 00:15:30,256
ye.

353
00:15:29,897 --> 00:15:31,236
vu zaynen zey geven?

354
00:15:30,938 --> 00:15:32,130
in KUŽIAI.

355
00:15:32,271 --> 00:15:35,674
iz Kleiba iz geven in Shavl tsu in Kuzh?

356
00:15:32,305 --> 00:15:33,159
gufe.

357
00:15:35,258 --> 00:15:38,036
in Kuzh iz er geven, in Kuzh.

358
00:15:36,304 --> 00:15:37,479
in Kuzh?

359
00:15:38,076 --> 00:15:39,842
nu zo-...

360
00:15:40,472 --> 00:15:44,010
bin ikh avek un er hot mir gezogt, zogt er: "UNK vos na dir UNK".

361
00:15:44,944 --> 00:15:48,532
"hob keyn fardros nisht, kum bay mir". "⟨neyn⟩", zog ikh: "bay dir gey ikh nit".

362
00:15:48,943 --> 00:15:50,388
vu s'iz a sakh,

363
00:15:51,357 --> 00:15:53,410
dortn iz a knape khasene.

364
00:15:54,833 --> 00:15:58,590
iz der iz der galekh KLEIBA, er hot oykhet oysgehaltn yidn?

365
00:15:57,921 --> 00:16:00,311
yo, KLEIBA hot oysgehaltn yidn.

366
00:16:00,722 --> 00:16:02,420
KLEIBA, er iz geshtorbn,

367
00:16:02,663 --> 00:16:04,040
a rak hot er gehat.

368
00:16:04,047 --> 00:16:05,627
shoyn nokh der milkhome?

369
00:16:05,076 --> 00:16:07,871
nokh di milkhome. er hot oysbahaltn a sakh.

370
00:16:07,590 --> 00:16:09,018
a sakh yidn, yo?

371
00:16:09,058 --> 00:16:10,942
efsher veyst ir umgefer vifl?

372
00:16:10,982 --> 00:16:15,734
vifl veys ikh nit, ober a sakh, vayl er hot nit, er hot avekgegebn in derfer, farshteyt?

373
00:16:16,112 --> 00:16:20,729
un der POŽĖLA flegt forn zukhn produktn.

374
00:16:20,584 --> 00:16:22,400
ver iz geven der POŽĖLA?

375
00:16:22,069 --> 00:16:23,328
oykh a galekh.

376
00:16:22,997 --> 00:16:24,324
fun vanent?

377
00:16:24,921 --> 00:16:27,311
iz in KUŽIAI zaynen geven tsvey galokhim?

378
00:16:26,794 --> 00:16:27,665
ye.

379
00:16:27,891 --> 00:16:29,471
POŽĖLA un KLEIBA?

380
00:16:29,072 --> 00:16:33,133
KLEIBA iz geven a g-, KLEBONAS, flegt men UNK...

381
00:16:31,485 --> 00:16:33,675
an elterere galekh, ye?

382
00:16:33,675 --> 00:16:35,225
un POŽĖLA iz geven?..

383
00:16:35,248 --> 00:16:39,916
ikh veys nit vos er iz dortn geven, veys ikh nit, ober a galekh. er hot dokh, lebt dokh nokh itster, POŽĖLA.

384
00:16:40,581 --> 00:16:45,047
iz ir ir hot ge- ay- v- v- ver hot aykh on- oysgeshribn di dokumentn?

385
00:16:45,475 --> 00:16:46,431
KLEIBA.

386
00:16:46,504 --> 00:16:48,422
KLEIBA hot aykh ongeshribn di doku-

387
00:16:47,432 --> 00:16:51,273
KLEIBA, di di er hot nit gevust fun mir, POŽĖLA, ikh hob fun im oykh nit gevust.

388
00:16:50,875 --> 00:16:53,822
ah, mit POŽĖLAn hot ir nisht gehat tsu ton, nor mit KLEIBAn.

389
00:16:52,731 --> 00:16:54,446
neyn, nor mir KLEIBAn.

390
00:16:54,283 --> 00:16:56,656
un ver zayt ir gevorn in di dokumentn?

391
00:16:57,574 --> 00:16:59,913
ayer nomen iz geven TEODORA...

392
00:16:59,262 --> 00:17:02,344
LEONGINA TEODORA ADOMAITYTĖ.

393
00:17:02,316 --> 00:17:05,263
dos heyst ir hot gehat tsvey tsvey nemen oykh, ye?

394
00:17:04,290 --> 00:17:05,246
ye.

395
00:17:05,505 --> 00:17:06,680
LEONGINA...

396
00:17:06,602 --> 00:17:08,790
TEODORA ADOMAITYTĖ.

397
00:17:08,863 --> 00:17:11,388
vi a nit keyn khasene gehate litvishe meydl?

398
00:17:11,175 --> 00:17:12,029
ye.

399
00:17:14,483 --> 00:17:18,358
un mit di dokumentn zayt ir gekumen vayter tsu KAUŠIENĖn?

400
00:17:19,309 --> 00:17:21,007
az ir hot gehat dem dokument?

401
00:17:20,118 --> 00:17:22,748
ikh hob gehat dem dokument, bin ikh geven bay KAU-...

402
00:17:22,748 --> 00:17:24,584
di der yinglekh zeyer geveynt.

403
00:17:24,692 --> 00:17:27,031
v- vemens yingl?

404
00:17:24,760 --> 00:17:27,673
"vu iz Lionia"? ir zun, ir zun.

405
00:17:27,730 --> 00:17:28,713
a yingl.

406
00:17:28,573 --> 00:17:30,339
KAUŠIENĖ hot gehat a yingl?

407
00:17:29,839 --> 00:17:31,740
ye, ot kh'hob do zayn bild.

408
00:17:32,033 --> 00:17:40,534
iz es, hot er geveynt, oder flegt nit esn keyn zakh nisht. zogt zi: "se geyt mir unter der kind, er est nit un veynt er".

409
00:17:40,534 --> 00:17:42,421
iz zi gekumen tsurik fun

410
00:17:42,765 --> 00:17:46,134
fun dem UNK, fun PETROŠIUSn un zi hot mir tsugenumen.

411
00:17:45,735 --> 00:17:47,973
a, un ir zayn dan geven bay PETROŠIUSn?

412
00:17:47,625 --> 00:17:52,428
ye, bin ikh tsurik gekumen bay PETROŠIUSn, UNK volt er gegangen andersh vu zukhn.

413
00:17:52,654 --> 00:17:55,972
iz zi gekumen, zogt zi: "kum, for aheym, UNK", zogt zi.

414
00:17:56,518 --> 00:17:58,942
 "for bay mir tsurik un fartik".

415
00:17:59,050 --> 00:18:03,296
zogt zi: "un ikh vel avekgeyn baym galekh un ikh vel zogn er zol zi yene baruikn".

416
00:18:03,538 --> 00:18:04,848
 vemen yene?

417
00:18:03,623 --> 00:18:06,148
UNK UNK a a kristin,

418
00:18:06,306 --> 00:18:09,253
zi ah voz zi krikht in yenems zakhn,

419
00:18:09,428 --> 00:18:12,521
heyst es, far vos zi zogt: "JI NEINA Į BAŽNYČIĄ".

420
00:18:12,521 --> 00:18:13,472
nu.

421
00:18:12,550 --> 00:18:14,754
a, un vos iz dos geven far a kristin?

422
00:18:14,355 --> 00:18:15,412
a shik-,

423
00:18:15,553 --> 00:18:16,664
UNK, a goye,

424
00:18:16,664 --> 00:18:19,040
a litvinke.

425
00:18:17,342 --> 00:18:19,141
ir hot gevust ver zi iz?

426
00:18:19,114 --> 00:18:20,053
ye.

427
00:18:21,274 --> 00:18:22,922
ir nomen gedenkt ir?

428
00:18:22,759 --> 00:18:24,457
dem nomen gedenk ikh nit.

429
00:18:25,071 --> 00:18:29,312
ŽILIKĖ, dem familye-nomen gedenk ikh, dem nomen gedenk ikh nit.

430
00:18:28,041 --> 00:18:29,553
vi zogt ir, ŽILYTĖ?

431
00:18:29,312 --> 00:18:30,515
ŽILIKĖ!

432
00:18:30,268 --> 00:18:32,692
ŽILIKĖ, hot men azoy ir gerufn, ye?

433
00:18:32,226 --> 00:18:34,281
ye, ⟨s'iz⟩ familye-nomen.

434
00:18:34,281 --> 00:18:36,742
der bruder iz geven a politsman.

435
00:18:37,272 --> 00:18:38,970
er hot zikh dershosn aleyn.

436
00:18:39,178 --> 00:18:41,112
nokh der milkhome tsu fa-?

437
00:18:39,212 --> 00:18:46,226
neyn, neyn, in mitn der milkhome hot getshistet dem, gereynikt dem

438
00:18:43,347 --> 00:18:44,522
gereynikt?

439
00:18:46,165 --> 00:18:47,323
dem biks?

440
00:18:46,266 --> 00:18:49,618
dem biks, hot er arayngelozn zikh in im.

441
00:18:49,371 --> 00:18:50,445
tsufelik.

442
00:18:51,328 --> 00:18:55,996
un di ŽILIKĖ hot gehat gehat pretenzyes far vos ir geyt nit in tifle?

443
00:18:55,530 --> 00:18:56,725
ye.

444
00:18:56,725 --> 00:18:57,820
nu...

445
00:18:59,715 --> 00:19:02,791
un az ir zayt gekumen tsu KAUŠIENĖn dem tsveytn mol,

446
00:19:02,791 --> 00:19:05,733
hot ir shoyn gehat dem dokument fun galekh fun?

447
00:19:04,677 --> 00:19:08,350
ikh hob gehat dem dokument, ober ver ver kukt dortn oyf dokument...

448
00:19:08,355 --> 00:19:10,340
UNK tsvishn, gehat dem dokument,

449
00:19:10,482 --> 00:19:13,648
vayle me fregt traybn fun dorf oykh, flegt men traybn in,

450
00:19:13,789 --> 00:19:15,757
in dos vi ruft zikh dortn,

451
00:19:15,882 --> 00:19:18,182
in Daytshland, oy, UNK fargesn...

452
00:19:18,182 --> 00:19:19,335
arbeter...

453
00:19:19,729 --> 00:19:20,972
in Saksonye?

454
00:19:19,813 --> 00:19:22,490
in Saksonye! in Saksonye...

455
00:19:23,188 --> 00:19:25,578
nu iz es,

456
00:19:28,453 --> 00:19:33,107
iz geven a SENIŪNAS vos er hot gehalt- zikh, gekhavert mitn,

457
00:19:33,107 --> 00:19:34,404
mit KAUŠISn.

458
00:19:34,782 --> 00:19:36,396
zogt er, "ikh vel ir nit ts-"

459
00:19:36,402 --> 00:19:39,180
vos, ver iz der SENIŪNAS, vos iz dos, a SENIŪNAS?

460
00:19:38,730 --> 00:19:42,270
a SENIŪNAS, nu in dorf iz do a SENIŪNAS, nu...

461
00:19:41,312 --> 00:19:43,314
a eltsterer, ye?

462
00:19:42,270 --> 00:19:49,642
an eltster oyfn dorf. hot er gebetn, zol zi zayn, zogt zi, vos vos UNK shikn. zogt er UNK, zogt er: "ikh vel nit shikn".

463
00:19:43,438 --> 00:19:44,799
an eltere, ye?

464
00:19:49,902 --> 00:19:53,743
UNK der dorf eltste- elterer hot gezogt az er vet aykh nit shikn?

465
00:19:53,142 --> 00:19:56,544
ye, hot er mir nit geshikt in... zogt er: "zol zi zayn bay dir".

466
00:19:57,276 --> 00:19:59,919
vosere arbetn flegt ir ton bay di KAUŠIENĖn?

467
00:19:59,622 --> 00:20:03,415
altsding vos me tut in a sh- in a shtub, altsding hob ikh geton.

468
00:20:03,415 --> 00:20:05,353
nor keyn ki hob ikh nit gekent melkn.

469
00:20:05,427 --> 00:20:08,858
vayter bay di khazeyrim un bay di ferd un forn mit di ferd

470
00:20:08,858 --> 00:20:10,820
un hey grebenen un...

471
00:20:11,350 --> 00:20:16,676
beshas me hot ge-, korn nemen, altsding, altsding hob ikh geton, un CUKRINIS, altsding hob ikh gearbet.

472
00:20:16,547 --> 00:20:18,599
dos heyst

473
00:20:19,095 --> 00:20:23,308
tsuk-, tsuker, oyf tsuker tsu baarbetn, ye... tsuker-burikes, ye?

474
00:20:20,226 --> 00:20:23,024
ye, burikes, tsuker-burikes.

475
00:20:23,024 --> 00:20:24,894
altsding, ikh hob gehorevet gut.

476
00:20:24,681 --> 00:20:27,206
ir kent ⟨UNK⟩deven mit a ferd?

477
00:20:26,908 --> 00:20:27,830
yo.

478
00:20:27,668 --> 00:20:31,813
ir kent forn oyf a ferd. dos hot ir gekent ir ayer shtetl shoyn?

479
00:20:31,380 --> 00:20:32,217
ye.

480
00:20:32,275 --> 00:20:34,311
ir ayer shtetl hot ir shoyn ge-

481
00:20:33,945 --> 00:20:35,879
raytn oyf a ferd, altsding.

482
00:20:35,498 --> 00:20:37,567
dos hot, ver hot aykh dos gelernt?

483
00:20:37,523 --> 00:20:39,207
di PETROŠIUS vayb.

484
00:20:39,207 --> 00:20:43,203
UNK zey zey hobn oykh gehat erd, flegn mir avekgeyn un far- UNK raytn oyfn ferd.

485
00:20:43,294 --> 00:20:46,427
dos iz lebn nokh in shtetl, zayendik kleyne meydlekh?

486
00:20:44,897 --> 00:20:46,764
ye.

487
00:20:47,209 --> 00:20:53,244
iz fun dem on fun dem on kent ir kent ir kent ir zikh ba- batsyen mit a ferd?

488
00:20:48,981 --> 00:20:50,260
ye, ken shoyn,

489
00:20:50,260 --> 00:20:51,321
aleding.

490
00:20:52,322 --> 00:20:55,826
nu yo, un dortn bin ikh shoyn geven biz tsu ende.

491
00:20:55,900 --> 00:20:58,779
⟨emetser⟩ hot shoyn gehat opgeshosn KAUŠISn.

492
00:20:58,583 --> 00:21:00,382
f-, ver hot im opgeshosn?

493
00:21:00,017 --> 00:21:01,023
daytshn.

494
00:21:01,198 --> 00:21:04,668
er hot ongenumen, s'iz gekumen fun Shavl eyner,

495
00:21:05,569 --> 00:21:06,828
un,

496
00:21:06,919 --> 00:21:08,803
dortn zikh zayn.

497
00:21:08,826 --> 00:21:14,743
veyst dokh, biz es vet ariber di krig, di di muter gebetn az zol er zayn.

498
00:21:13,517 --> 00:21:15,333
ver iz geven der eyner?

499
00:21:15,458 --> 00:21:17,106
a litviner oykh.

500
00:21:16,842 --> 00:21:18,557
a bakanter fun KAUŠAS?

501
00:21:17,567 --> 00:21:20,733
neyn, fun KAUŠISn a bakanter, fun KAUŠIENĖ.

502
00:21:21,330 --> 00:21:24,969
nu, iz bay nakht iz er gegangen, me hot geshosn zeyer

503
00:21:25,009 --> 00:21:25,880
fil.

504
00:21:26,376 --> 00:21:28,597
un me hot oysgeleygt nayn daytshn.

505
00:21:30,190 --> 00:21:35,721
nu zaynen gekumen di daytshn tsu loyfn, zogn zey: "fun der zayt hobn mit gehert shiseray".

506
00:21:35,721 --> 00:21:38,604
un ot undzere khaveyrim hot men avekgeleygt nayn shtik.

507
00:21:38,627 --> 00:21:40,899
hot men im aroysgetribn un me hot im dershosn.

508
00:21:41,850 --> 00:21:43,649
un er iz gor nit shuldik geven.

509
00:21:44,753 --> 00:21:46,485
hot men dershosn KAUŠISn.

510
00:21:46,575 --> 00:21:48,948
ver hot dortn geshosn iz nisht bavust?

511
00:21:49,360 --> 00:21:53,623
UNK mistome ver es hot geshosn, mistome fun vald, UNK dokh gelebt in a vald.

512
00:21:53,899 --> 00:21:57,926
a vald iz derbay geven, hobn mir dortn gelebt.

513
00:21:58,455 --> 00:22:03,562
nokh dem in der fri kumt arayn a daytsh, un kukt in di okopes bay undz, altsding.

514
00:22:03,096 --> 00:22:04,794
in di shuts-griber, ye?

515
00:22:04,277 --> 00:22:06,026
in shuts-keler iz geven.

516
00:22:06,083 --> 00:22:07,764
zogt er...

517
00:22:09,897 --> 00:22:22,851
vos vos vos, zog ikh: "mir veysn nit vu di vu der foter", ikh hob gezogt "der foter", zog ikh: "der foter iz iz er geven", zog ikh, "mit undz", me hot im aroysgetribn, zog ikh: "vu iz er?". "er vet kumen", zogt er.

518
00:22:23,228 --> 00:22:27,862
nu nokh dem zog tsum daytshn: "vart, ikh vel geyn onklaybn eyer".

519
00:22:28,105 --> 00:22:34,303
in dortn in DARŽINĖ. zogt er: "nu gey UNK".

520
00:22:32,138 --> 00:22:34,005
in shayer, in shayer, yo?

521
00:22:34,303 --> 00:22:38,746
zogt er: "nu gey". gey ikh aroyf un ikh shray: "KAUŠAS, KAUŠAS, KAUŠAS!"

522
00:22:39,057 --> 00:22:42,139
"TĖVAI, TĖVAI", zog UNK...

523
00:22:40,137 --> 00:22:41,515
s'iz "foter", ye?

524
00:22:42,415 --> 00:22:46,914
"foter". keyner entfert zikh nit. keyner entfert zikh, heyst es az er iz nito.

525
00:22:47,275 --> 00:22:50,036
nokh dem vi mir zaynen antlofn fun dortn -

526
00:22:50,110 --> 00:22:52,427
hobn mir gedarft aroysforn fun dortn -

527
00:22:52,427 --> 00:22:54,325
zey hobn glaykh tseshosn di shtub,

528
00:22:54,325 --> 00:22:56,178
untergetsundn zeyere

529
00:22:56,235 --> 00:23:00,211
un mir hobn gedarft antloyfn. az mir zaynen antlofn

530
00:23:00,808 --> 00:23:06,590
az mir zaynen shoyn gekumen oyf tsurik, umgefer a fir vokhn...

531
00:23:06,900 --> 00:23:08,649
forn mir shoyn aheym

532
00:23:09,145 --> 00:23:12,969
fun vaytn ze ikh, zog ikh UNK, s'iz do shoyn di shtub nito dayne

533
00:23:14,325 --> 00:23:18,200
zog ikh, un oyfn vegn trefn mir eynem

534
00:23:18,477 --> 00:23:22,791
zogn zey, KAUŠISn hot men opgeshosn, du veyst vu er ligt, dayn man?

535
00:23:22,847 --> 00:23:25,440
zogt zi: "vu?" zogt er: "hintern KLOJIMA".

536
00:23:25,885 --> 00:23:28,359
epes hintern hi- shtroy-shayer.

537
00:23:27,977 --> 00:23:29,473
hintern ⟨sharaye⟩.

538
00:23:29,665 --> 00:23:32,072
nu bin ikh tsugegangen,

539
00:23:32,736 --> 00:23:35,390
hob ikh a kuk geton, zog ikh, yo, er iz dos.

540
00:23:35,390 --> 00:23:37,438
vayle dortn iz fule umgeshosene,

541
00:23:37,714 --> 00:23:40,053
daytshn un rusn un vos ir vilt.

542
00:23:40,093 --> 00:23:42,495
zog ikh, dos iz es, ot trogt er mayn hemd.

543
00:23:42,495 --> 00:23:44,149
dem mans hemd di zaydene.

544
00:23:44,149 --> 00:23:48,325
s'iz geven heys, zog ikh: "vos darfstu trogn di layvntene hemd?"

545
00:23:48,325 --> 00:23:51,276
ikh hob aroysgenumen fun tshemodan mayn mans a hemd

546
00:23:51,298 --> 00:23:55,983
un ikh hob gegebn im onton, zog ikh: "tu zikh on, s'iz dokh azoy heys".

547
00:23:56,361 --> 00:24:01,417
nu hot er zikh ongeton dortn un mir hobn ⟨im⟩ baerdikt in KUŽIAI.

548
00:24:01,491 --> 00:24:04,505
un a galekh iz gekumen tsu baerdikn?

549
00:24:04,579 --> 00:24:06,767
mitn galekh hot ir im baerdikt?

550
00:24:06,958 --> 00:24:09,027
ver iz gekumen, KLEIBA?

551
00:24:09,135 --> 00:24:12,588
neyn, an anderer, dukht mir, an anderer, dos gedenk ikh nit.

552
00:24:13,050 --> 00:24:15,069
mir hobn baerdikt

553
00:24:15,345 --> 00:24:19,895
me hot gemakht an eynfakhe trune, s'iz nit geven vu, s'iz dokh der di krig iz dokh nokh gegangen.

554
00:24:20,155 --> 00:24:24,097
nu un me hot im baerdikt. ikh veys vu di l- vu der KAPINĖS iz un...

555
00:24:23,614 --> 00:24:25,430
v- vu der besoylem, yo?

556
00:24:24,846 --> 00:24:28,350
ye, itster zi iz geshtorbn mit fir yor tsurik,

557
00:24:28,963 --> 00:24:30,324
bin ikh geforn

558
00:24:30,752 --> 00:24:32,242
in di KAPINĖS.

559
00:24:31,731 --> 00:24:33,868
in dem, in dem besoylem?

560
00:24:32,242 --> 00:24:33,209
ye.

561
00:24:33,300 --> 00:24:35,356
oyfn besoylem UNK vayle zi,

562
00:24:35,356 --> 00:24:41,243
zi hot farn shtarbn hot zi gezogt, me zol UNK me zol on- nor az ir zolt zayn bay di bayn...

563
00:24:41,434 --> 00:24:47,013
bay di levaye. ikh bin gekumen, ikh bin geven oyfn tifle bin ikh geven, nu UNK bin ikh geven dortn oyfn besoylem.

564
00:24:47,104 --> 00:24:52,532
az ven hot zikh di, ir hot gezogt di KAUŠIENĖn az ir zayt a yidishe?

565
00:24:52,453 --> 00:24:56,092
nokh dem hob ikh shoyn, zi hot zikh shoyn dervust, der galekh hot ir gezogt.

566
00:24:53,483 --> 00:24:54,591
ven?

567
00:24:56,470 --> 00:24:59,940
der galekh hot ir gezogt in der tsayt fun der milkhome az zayt ir a yidishe?

568
00:24:59,845 --> 00:25:02,792
ye, shoyn az ikh hob shoyn...

569
00:25:02,950 --> 00:25:06,844
gevust zi, zi hot shoyn gevust, zi hot gezogt: "UNK un du darfst oyshaltn".

570
00:25:06,844 --> 00:25:08,515
"nit meyn", zogt er,

571
00:25:08,515 --> 00:25:10,574
"az vos du shteyst in tifle

572
00:25:10,574 --> 00:25:14,253
ayngeboygnt zikh", zogt er, "un du bukst zikh far Yezusn",

573
00:25:14,253 --> 00:25:17,439
zogt er: "dos iz alts, me darf helfn mentshn",

574
00:25:18,154 --> 00:25:19,160
zogt er,

575
00:25:19,318 --> 00:25:20,223
nu,

576
00:25:20,938 --> 00:25:22,450
keyn zakh nit gezogt.

577
00:25:22,980 --> 00:25:25,370
iz, der galekh hot ayngeredt, ye?

578
00:25:24,769 --> 00:25:31,310
ye, zogt er: "un zi, zi loyft in ergets nit, zi iz a ruike", zogt er. "du vilst nit UNK, kum bay mir, ikh nem ir tsu", zogt er, "ale mol".

579
00:25:32,295 --> 00:25:38,330
un ikh hob nit gevolt, vayle er hot dokh mir nit gezogt az es zaynen do a sakh yidishe, un ikh hob gevust shoyn.

580
00:25:38,573 --> 00:25:40,086
un az s'iz do a sakh,

581
00:25:40,260 --> 00:25:41,699
du vest arbetn

582
00:25:41,699 --> 00:25:43,151
un zey ⟨veln⟩ kukn

583
00:25:43,151 --> 00:25:44,574
UNK vey ton der harts.

584
00:25:44,682 --> 00:25:47,511
un az ikh bin eyner aleyn, veyst ir, ikh darf horeven far

585
00:25:47,618 --> 00:25:51,240
ot azoy mayner geven. un ikh hob gevust, vu s'iz a sakh do, toyg nit.

586
00:25:53,608 --> 00:25:58,321
ir gedenkt dem moment vi di daytshn zaynen avek fun Lite?

587
00:25:58,321 --> 00:26:00,116
un s'iz gekumen der royt armey?

588
00:26:00,190 --> 00:26:03,846
yo, dos gedenk ikh totshne, keyn mol volt dos nit far-

589
00:26:02,721 --> 00:26:04,419
vi iz dos ge-, forgekumen?

590
00:26:03,868 --> 00:26:04,942
azoy.

591
00:26:04,948 --> 00:26:05,974
s'iz...

592
00:26:05,974 --> 00:26:10,927
mir zaynen geven aroysgetribn zeyer vayt, vayt UNK dortn, oyf ŠAUKĖNAI, ikh veys nit dortn di...

593
00:26:10,927 --> 00:26:13,026
vayter, hinter KUŽIAI, zeyer vayt.

594
00:26:12,627 --> 00:26:14,376
ver hot aykh aroysgetribn?

595
00:26:15,158 --> 00:26:18,982
nu az mir zenen aroys fun KUŽIAI, hobn mir dokh gemuzt avekgeyn, vu nit iz zayn.

596
00:26:18,651 --> 00:26:20,872
un ver hot aykh geheysn aroysgeyn fun KUŽIAI?

597
00:26:20,372 --> 00:26:23,049
di daytshn! "fun dem ort muzt ir aroysgeyn!"

598
00:26:23,173 --> 00:26:24,753
zaynen mir avek

599
00:26:26,295 --> 00:26:27,689
dortn

600
00:26:27,865 --> 00:26:30,407
un mir zaynen arayn in a...

601
00:26:30,463 --> 00:26:31,739
bay eynem a,

602
00:26:31,915 --> 00:26:33,191
a PONAS.

603
00:26:33,332 --> 00:26:35,244
ah ah a porets, ye?

604
00:26:34,885 --> 00:26:36,853
ye. a raykher.

605
00:26:35,244 --> 00:26:36,550
a raykher mentsh?

606
00:26:37,669 --> 00:26:39,201
zogt er:

607
00:26:39,201 --> 00:26:40,936
"nu UNK tsunemen".

608
00:26:40,977 --> 00:26:44,396
"mir hobn oykh gehat a ŪKIS, mit altsding", zogt er.

609
00:26:43,778 --> 00:26:45,257
a virtshaft, yo?

610
00:26:44,503 --> 00:26:49,188
a virtshaft mit mit land, mit altsding, me hot undz alts farbrent un mir hore-

611
00:26:49,600 --> 00:26:52,142
zogt er: "di meydl volt ikh tsunemen".

612
00:26:52,789 --> 00:26:54,369
di meydl dos iz ir?

613
00:26:54,055 --> 00:26:55,179
dos bin ikh.

614
00:26:56,113 --> 00:27:10,892
nu zog ikh zog ikh: "neyn, vi UNK lozn di brider mit di mame, mit di boben", zog ikh, "un ikh vel do blaybn". zog ikh: "neyn, lomir avek vayter". UNK eyne zogt zi: "ot UNK in dem tsimerl"; zogt zi, "zayt ale". zog ikh: "s'iz gut".

615
00:27:10,892 --> 00:27:12,864
alts eyns UNK do lang nit zayn.

616
00:27:13,613 --> 00:27:16,746
vifl mentshn zayt ir dan geven, ir, KAUŠIENĖ?..

617
00:27:16,836 --> 00:27:18,028
KAUŠIENĖn,

618
00:27:18,203 --> 00:27:19,851
tsvey kinder,

619
00:27:20,110 --> 00:27:21,488
di bobe,

620
00:27:22,978 --> 00:27:24,288
un nokh a tante.

621
00:27:24,497 --> 00:27:26,786
di bobe dos iz KAUŠIENĖs muter?

622
00:27:26,202 --> 00:27:27,090
ye.

623
00:27:28,952 --> 00:27:31,815
di di kinder zaynen shoyn geven greyse tsu kleyne?

624
00:27:31,298 --> 00:27:36,658
nit keyn kl-, nit keyn, nu der der eyner hot gemuzt zayn tsen yor un der tsveyter

625
00:27:36,900 --> 00:27:38,171
a tsvelf yor,

626
00:27:38,171 --> 00:27:39,932
tsvelf, draytsn yor UNK.

627
00:27:41,845 --> 00:27:46,041
un azoy azoy hot ir farblibn bay di froy vos zi hot aykh arayngelozn?

628
00:27:45,895 --> 00:27:53,145
ye, zaynen mir geven, me hot gevart biz di rusn veln onkumen. nokh dem kumt on eyner tsu forn, a litviner.

629
00:27:53,472 --> 00:27:54,748
zogt er:

630
00:27:55,024 --> 00:27:56,638
"ir veyst vos?"

631
00:27:57,336 --> 00:27:59,979
"GALĖSI, ir vet kenen bald forn aheym."

632
00:28:00,593 --> 00:28:05,362
zog ikh: "v- vos?" zogt er: "dortn oyfn barg raytn shoyn di di rusn".

633
00:28:05,875 --> 00:28:08,198
zog UNK zog ikh, "nu, s'iz shoyn gut", zog ikh.

634
00:28:08,440 --> 00:28:12,028
nem di ferd beyde, mir hobn gehat di ferd mitgenumen

635
00:28:12,034 --> 00:28:14,508
mitn vogn, zog ikh, un mir veln forn aheym,

636
00:28:14,515 --> 00:28:15,876
do oyf KUŽIAI.

637
00:28:16,118 --> 00:28:19,419
nu un ikh veys dokh az ikh vel dortn oykh nit zayn, ikh vel forn in Shavl.

638
00:28:20,303 --> 00:28:21,430
nu iz,

639
00:28:21,430 --> 00:28:22,847
zaynen mir gekumen,

640
00:28:22,847 --> 00:28:24,262
s'iz take arayn di rusn.

641
00:28:24,336 --> 00:28:25,969
iz es far dem

642
00:28:25,969 --> 00:28:27,522
iz geshtanen eyner

643
00:28:27,522 --> 00:28:29,240
baym bay brunem

644
00:28:29,247 --> 00:28:30,844
er hot ge⟨UNK⟩t a daytsh.

645
00:28:31,407 --> 00:28:35,791
zogt er:" vu fort m-, vu raytn ale daytshn, vu iz do oyf oyf Daytshland?"

646
00:28:35,791 --> 00:28:37,628
veyst zi nit, zi farshteyt nit.

647
00:28:39,507 --> 00:28:42,032
fort er vayter bin ikh, shtey baym brunem.

648
00:28:43,067 --> 00:28:48,548
zogt er: "vu fort men, vu zol ikh raytn oyf Daytshland?" zog ikh: "do!", nit ikh veys vu...

649
00:28:48,548 --> 00:28:50,216
nit ikh veys ven..

650
00:28:50,509 --> 00:28:52,345
ir hot er glaykh ongeknakt,

651
00:28:52,345 --> 00:28:53,439
opgeshosn.

652
00:28:53,783 --> 00:28:54,489
vemen?

653
00:28:54,373 --> 00:28:56,155
di litvine, di meydl.

654
00:28:56,280 --> 00:28:58,434
un ikh hob gezogt oyf dortn,

655
00:28:58,963 --> 00:29:00,158
bin ikh geblibn lebn.

